How much does ease of ordering matter to restaurant customers?

Toast and Google announced a new partnership that allows guests to order directly from google and google maps.

Shawn RIFs on how this integration is a game changer and how it will increase sales as well as save restaurants money.

In the full episode (RIF007) we RIF on how this new technology will make things frictionless, how tech companies need to “speak restaurant”, and how it could increase revenue. 

Restaurant Idea Factory (aka “RIF”) hosted by Kyle, Shawn, Jensen, airs weekly Fridays at 4pm ET. Presented by 7shifts, Marqii and Ovation.

Dishwasher to Restaurant Owner... His Secret to Millions Revealed!
